This OE is an ode to the 2 metas that have occurred over the past 3 weeks. 

Yuga Labs released their Dookey Dash game which led Crypto Natives to spiral into a gaming competition for a skills-based mint.

Simultaneously a new meta led by Jack Butcher from Visualize Value was capturing the zeitgeist with his VV Checks.

This is a point in time where NFTs have captured people and evoked emotions that were foreign before this point in time.

This OE it dedicated to remembering the moments. It is free. There is no utility aside from art and possibility for future engagement.

*This is limited to 3 per wallet. If you mint more than 1, we ask that you give the two others to friends as gifts. Friends who were involved with you in at least one of these metas are friends worth cherishing p+6
